<para id="fs-idm244632064">The diagram also shows the departments that report to the production unit director and gives an indication as to the flow of goods through production. The flow of goods through production is more evident in <link target-id="OSX_Acct_M04_01_DVFactory"/>, which depicts Dinosaur Vinyl as a simple factory with three stages of production.</para>
