<para id="fs-idm236903744"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68123"/>Which of the following is a conversion cost?</para>
<list id="fs-idm216306400" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>raw materials</item>
<item>direct materials</item>
<item>administrative expenses</item>
<item>factory depreciation expenses</item>
