<exercise id="fs-idm242695728">
<problem id="fs-idm242796288">
<para id="fs-idm223401376"><link class="lo-reference" document="m68123"/>During production, to what are the costs in job order costing applied?</para>
<list id="fs-idm244493184" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
